thread.title: Genesis Dorsey

author: Genesis Dorsey
title: Genesis Dorsey
text: I was really nervous about ordering my first set of boxes from any company. However, after researching all of my options, Packlane seemed to be the only choice for me. The setup was so easy and it came extremely fast. I can't say enough how much I love my boxes. I have been getting compliments from all of my supporters and I've already referred friends and other business owners. The pricing was budget friendly and I really don't think you can beat these prices with this level of customization. I will be ordering again and again and again.
